--ENG--

  The task was to gain access to a restricted web portal using the email ctf-player@picoctf.org. Since the password was unknown, the goal was to find a developer's "backdoor" or a hidden entry point mentioned in the challenge description.

Solution Steps
Source Code Inspection: By inspecting the page source (CTRL+U), I discovered a hidden comment:
